<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/28532755-bayou-des-cannes-cajun"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1599724094i/28532755._UY100_CR16,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/28532755-bayou-des-cannes-cajun">Bayou des Cannes Cajun</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Library. If not currently in your local library&apos;s collection then request interlibrary loan. Library will locate and borrow the book from another libr<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Library. If not currently in your local library's collection then request interlibrary loan. Library will locate and borrow the book from another library for you. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
