        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2670131749" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2057455137124513494"><b>1.5 Stars</b><br/><br/>Apparently, Hollywood ego is just not my cuppa, and I really couldn&apos;t motivate myself to care much about an insecure actress struggling with self acceptance and being happy. <br/><br/>I will give credit to the acerbic, smartly funny wit. However, the last chapter was the best and that&apos;s a long journey to go to get some goodness.<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText2057455137124513494" style="display:none"><b>1.5 Stars</b><br /><br />Apparently, Hollywood ego is just not my cuppa, and I really couldn't motivate myself to care much about an insecure actress struggling with self acceptance and being happy. <br /><br />I will give credit to the acerbic, smartly funny wit. However, the last chapter was the best and that's a long journey to go to get some goodness.<br /></span>
