<span id="freeTextContainer1982948313409322247">It was okay. I like how it started but it felt like a bunch of tangents after awhile</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review3319983754">
