<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer7174119524831673792">Carrie Fisher was an American actress, screenwriter and author, most famous for her portrayal of Princess Leia in the original <i>Star Wars</i> trilogy. Fisher was the daughter of singer <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/351430._Eddie_Fisher' title=' Eddie Fisher' rel='nofollow noopener'> Eddie Fisher</a> and actress <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/223415._Debbie_Reynolds' title=' Debbie Reynolds' rel='nofollow noopener'> Debbie Reynolds</a>. She had one daughter, Billie Lourd (b. 1992). <br/><br/>Her final film, <i>Star Wars: The Last Jedi</i>, was released on December 15, 2017 and is dedicated to her.</span>
  <span id="freeText7174119524831673792" style="display:none">Carrie Fisher was an American actress, screenwriter and author, most famous for her portrayal of Princess Leia in the original <i>Star Wars</i> trilogy. Fisher was the daughter of singer <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/351430._Eddie_Fisher" title=" Eddie Fisher" rel="nofollow noopener"> Eddie Fisher</a> and actress <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/223415._Debbie_Reynolds" title=" Debbie Reynolds" rel="nofollow noopener"> Debbie Reynolds</a>. She had one daughter, Billie Lourd (b. 1992). <br /><br />Her final film, <i>Star Wars: The Last Jedi</i>, was released on December 15, 2017 and is dedicated to her.</span>
